	<p class="permlink"><a href="http://24ways.org/2009/rock-solid-html-emails#c003650" id="c003650">15/12/2009</a></p>
	<h4><a href=""><img src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=ae97212ed61df3766263d5a34f810aff&amp;size=100&amp;default=http%3A%2F%2Fcloud.24ways.org%2Fimg%2Fgravatar.png" class="gravatar" alt="" height="100" width="100" /> Gregory <small></small></a></h4>
		<p>Perfect.  Definitely the best article about html emails I&#8217;ve ever read.</p>


